# Setup

1. Clone the project which will make two projects/folders in your working directory
2. The projects will be client and server which are frontend and backend respectively
3. Place the .env file in "server" folder
4. Make a database locally and replace the DATABASE_URL link in .env with your database connection url
5. You are ready to run the projects

# Running the projects
For server, open the terminal and run the following commands:
    1. npm i
    2. npx prisma migrate dev
    3. npx prisma generate
    4. npm run dev
For client, open the terminal and run the following commands:
    1. npm i
    2. npm run dev